text: Men Without Wings () is a 1946 Czech World War II drama movie directed by František Čáp and starring Gustav Nezval, Ladislav H. Struna, Jaroslav Zrotal, Vladimír Hlavatý, Jan W. Speerger. ==Other websites== * Category:1946 drama movies Category:1946 war movies Category:Czech drama movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by František Čáp
